# В равностороннем треугольнике $ABC$ проведена биссектриса $AD$. Расстояние от точки $D$ до прямой $АС$ равно 6 см. Найдите расстояние от вершины $А$ до прямой $ВС$.  
scene "Equilateral ABC; bisector AD; dist(D, AC)=6; find dist(A, BC)"
layout canonical=triangle_ABC scale=1
points A, B, C, D, E, H

# Equilateral: AB = BC = CA
triangle A-B-C
equal-segments (A-B; B-C)
equal-segments (B-C; C-A)

# Angle bisector AD meets BC at D
intersect (angle-bisector B-A-C) with (segment B-C) at D

# The given distance from D to line AC is 6:
# Drop the perpendicular from D to AC at E, then set DE = 6
foot E from D to A-C
segment D-E [length=6, label="6"]

# Target: distance from A to line BC (the altitude AH)
foot H from A to B-C
target length A-H [label="?"]
